href="erct-001I.xml"
addr="erct-001I"
title="Proposition">proposition</fr:link>;</fr:li>
  <fr:li>for <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n \geq  0]]></fr:tex>, a type <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:em><fr:strong><html:span
xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span></fr:strong></fr:em> when for every <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[x,y:A]]></fr:tex> the identification type <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[x=y]]></fr:tex> is <html:span
xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n-1]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span>.</fr:li></fr:ul><fr:p>So, in particular, a <fr:tex
